				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-6f77bc3e elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="6f77bc3e" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
					<h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Challenges, or as we call them - opportunities. </h2>				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-6a87412d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text_grid" data-id="6a87412d" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text_grid.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<div id="text-grid-69ef9a0b9c334" class="text-grid"><div class="text-grid-item item-box"><h3>Integrating IT and OT for seamless production</h3><p>Integrating digital and operational technologies remains a major hurdle. Aligning data, systems, and teams across factory floors and enterprise IT environments requires deep technical and organizational transformation. </p><a class="item-link" href="#"></a></div><div class="text-grid-item item-box"><h3>Managing complexity across ecosystems </h3><p>Smart Manufacturing depends on the connected ecosystems of suppliers, platforms, and technologies. Orchestrating these networks securely and effectively is becoming a new core capability. </p><a class="item-link" href="#"></a></div><div class="text-grid-item item-box"><h3>Balancing innovation and cost pressure </h3><p>Economic uncertainty and investment constraints make it challenging to advance digital initiatives while maintaining cost efficiency and operational performance. </p><a class="item-link" href="#"></a></div><div class="text-grid-item item-box"><h3>Building future-ready skills and mindsets </h3><p>The shift toward data-driven production requires new competencies and cultural change – from engineering expertise to agile, cross-functional collaboration. </p><a class="item-link" href="#"></a></div><div class="text-grid-item item-box"><h3>Cybersecurity: protecting connected production environments </h3><p>The increasing connectivity of machines and processes creates new attack surfaces. A robust security strategy is crucial to safeguard production operations and minimize cyber risks. </p><a class="item-link" href="#"></a></div></div>                    <style>
                        .text-grid {
                            display: grid;
                            gap: 12px;
                            grid-template-columns: repeat(1, 1fr);
                        }

                        .text-grid-item {
                            display: flex;
                            flex-direction: column;
                        }

                        .hidden-item {
                            display: none;
                        }

                        @media (min-width: 768px) {
                            .text-grid {
                                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
                                gap: 24px;
                            }
                        }

                        @media (min-width: 1040px) {
                            .text-grid {
                                grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
                                gap: 32px;
                            }
                            .text-grid-item {
                                padding-bottom: 24px;
                            }
                        }
                    </style>

                    <script>
                        (function($){
                            $(document).ready(function(){
                                // Prevent double binding
                                $('.text-grid-toggle-button').off('click.textGrid').on('click.textGrid', function(e){
                                    e.preventDefault();

                                    const $button = $(this);
                                    const $wrap   = $button.closest('.text-grid-show-more');
                                    const target  = $wrap.data('target');            // e.g. "#text-grid-64f..."
                                    const $grid   = $(target);
                                    const $text   = $button.find('.text-grid-toggle-text');
                                    const $hiddenItems = $grid.find('.hidden-item'); // <-- scoped to this grid only

                                    $hiddenItems.toggle();

                                    const showMoreText = 'Show More +';
                                    const showLessText = 'Show Less -';

                                    const expanded = $button.attr('aria-expanded') === 'true';
                                    $button.attr('aria-expanded', expanded ? 'false' : 'true');
                                    $text.text(expanded ? showMoreText : showLessText);
                                });
                            });
                        })(jQuery);
                    </script>
                    				</div>
				</div>
