			<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="17" viewBox="0 0 20 17" fill="none"><path d="M1.5 2.25V7.75C1.5 8.1875 1.8125 8.5 2.25 8.5H3.75C4.15625 8.5 4.5 8.84375 4.5 9.25V9.875L6.3125 8.625C6.4375 8.5625 6.59375 8.5 6.75 8.5H10.75C11.1562 8.5 11.5 8.1875 11.5 7.75V2.25C11.5 1.84375 11.1562 1.5 10.75 1.5H2.25C1.8125 1.5 1.5 1.84375 1.5 2.25ZM2.25 0H10.75C11.9688 0 13 1.03125 13 2.25V7.75C13 9 11.9688 10 10.75 10H6.96875L4.15625 11.875C3.9375 12.0312 3.625 12.0625 3.375 11.9375C3.125 11.7812 3 11.5312 3 11.25V10H2.25C1 10 0 9 0 7.75V2.25C0 1.03125 1 0 2.25 0ZM8 11.75V11H9.5V11.75C9.5 12.1875 9.8125 12.5 10.25 12.5H13.25C13.375 12.5 13.5312 12.5625 13.6562 12.625L15.5 13.875V13.25C15.5 12.8438 15.8125 12.5 16.25 12.5H17.75C18.1562 12.5 18.5 12.1875 18.5 11.75V6.25C18.5 5.84375 18.1562 5.5 17.75 5.5H14V4H17.75C18.9688 4 20 5.03125 20 6.25V11.75C20 13 18.9688 14 17.75 14H17V15.25C17 15.5312 16.8438 15.7812 16.5938 15.9375C16.3438 16.0625 16.0625 16.0312 15.8125 15.875L13 14H10.25C9 14 8 13 8 11.75Z" fill="white"></path></svg>			</div>
